"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-comment-podcasts-paris-olympics-2024-your-essential-guide-b1172970.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Comment|Podcasts  Listen here on your chosen podcast platform.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The wait is nearly over.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Evening Standard's Sports Correspondent, Matt Majundie, joins us from Paris to give youthe definitive guide on everything you need to know about this year's Games.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.367739287916103e-12, \"text\": \"Evening Standard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\"}, {\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999454782952, \"rank\": 5.4521627373826676e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Team GB's chances of topping the medal table, the big name athletes competing again, to the rising stars to watch out for, and the key dates for your diary.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999413455711165, \"rank\": 5.8261919106486865e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In part two, our Arts Correspondent, Robert Dex, runs through the latest news from the Olympics, from Charlotte Dujardin's dramatic withdrawal, to Tom Daley testing out the beds in the athletes' village, and all the rumours around what to expect from the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}, {\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.153674373921798e-26, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Do